Insert into a list

Input: Data to be inserted, position at which to insert
Output: Edited list (No RETURNED output.)

If supplied position < 0 OR > number of elements in list:
    throw IndexOutOfBoundsException

if count equals length of array:
    Grow array

Copy X elements starting from specific position in array
INTO position + 1 in array
Where X is count - position
Code equivalent: System.arraycopy(data, pos, data, pos+1, (count-pos);

Insert value into position in array